<div id="bookmedr">
<strong>The Library Journal names The Book of Spies one of the Best Books of the Year! TWICE!</strong></p>
<p>&#8220;A master of the espionage thriller &#8230; a thrilling, spy-laden, history-rich page-turner.&#8221; Gayle is honored that the critics of the journal have chosen <em>The Book of Spies</em> as one of the top books of 2011 &#8211; both in print, and in audio. </p>
<p><em>The Book of Spies</em> is the prequel to <em>The Assassins</em>. </p>
